<ab facs="#facs_44_r1l21">ʒu <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> / <expan>Hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Neẅſtett<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> dem wır <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
