<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Lazan, <expan>hawbtm<ex>an</ex></expan>
                        zu Presslaw</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
<expan>hawbtm<ex>an</ex></expan>, als ir uns auf
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> brief <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
                        und ge<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> habt, wie ir mit den Colobraten geredt
                        und sie ewch ge<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>Newstett<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem wir <expan>befolhe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, mit ew <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> zu
                        reden. Et <expan>roga<ex>mus</ex></expan> in <expan>for<ex>ma</ex></expan>
                        credencie. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>vinc<ex>u</ex>la</expan> Petri.</ab>
</div>
